* HELO transaction -- pure layout; the REXX program supplies every value
* via SEND MAP FROM(stem.) — see runtime/rexx/hello.rexx.
MAP HELO1 SIZE 24x80
  FIELD INFOLINE AT 0,0   LEN 78 PROT BRIGHT COLOR=TURQUOISE
  FIELD GREETING AT 5,5 LEN 20 PROT BRIGHT COLOR=WHITE
  FIELD FOOTER   AT 23,2  LEN 60 PROT DIM    COLOR=BLUE
ENDMAP
